OL,3,CCastle Douglas man who lost two wives
OL,4,Cto cancer fundraising for local
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FA man from Castle Douglas who has lost
OL,8,Ftwo wives to cancer is rising money
OL,9,Ffor his local hospital as a 'thank
OL,10,Fyou' to NHS staff.
OL,12,FJim McLelland from Crossmichael lost
OL,13,Fhis first wife to cancer in 1994. His
OL,14,Fsecond died in the Dumfries and
OL,15,FGalloway Royal Infirmary last year.
OL,17,FHe's organising a festival for the
OL,18,Flocal community, where he'll run, walk
OL,19,Fand jog for 12 hours matching the
OL,20,Fstandard shift time for a member of
OL,21,FNHS staff.
