OL,7,FMr McLelland said: "The One Big Thank
OL,8,FYou is really a thank you to all of
OL,9,Fthe staff that work at the hospital.
OL,11,F"You've got the volunteers, you've got
OL,12,Fthe receptionists, there's the
OL,13,Fcleaners, there's the porters there's
OL,14,Fthe chemists, there's all these people
OL,15,Fthat work there that we don't see.
OL,17,F"These are the people we're thanking.
OL,19,F"I've lost somebody that was dear to
OL,20,Fme, you've just got to get on with
OL,21,Flife.
