OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"When Ruth passed away I didn't have
OL,8,Fall these things to occupy my mind, so
OL,9,Fyou just soldier through.
OL,11,F"I felt that this was one way of
OL,12,Fsaying thank you to all the staff that
OL,13,Fhad helped me get through it.
OL,15,F"It is our hospital and we've really
OL,16,Fgot to look after it."
