OL,7,FThe 'One Big Thank you' will place on
OL,8,Fthe 28th July 2024 when people are
OL,9,Fbeing encourage to hold their own
OL,10,Ffundraisers for the cause, before
OL,11,Fcelebrating at the One Big Thank You
OL,12,Fevent at Carlingwark Park, Castle
OL,13,FDouglas.
OL,15,FLocal organisations are also getting
OL,16,Finvolved in the fundraiser such as the
OL,17,FLoch Ken Trust and Castle Douglas
OL,18,FDevelopment Forum offering support to
OL,19,FMr McLelland ahead of the event next
OL,20,Fweekend.
