OL,7,FAmanda Burney from the Castle Douglas
OL,8,FDevelopment Forum said: "We'd taken on
OL,9,Fall the stuff of organising it, where
OL,10,Fits going to be etc and let Jim go out
OL,11,Fand about to the communities to get
OL,12,Fthe awareness out there.
OL,14,F"So hopefully lots of people will turn
OL,15,Fup on the day for a brilliant event"
