OL,7,FBarney Fryer from the Loch Ken Trust
OL,8,Fsaid: "Communities getting involved in
OL,9,Fall sorts of different ways. Jim is an
OL,10,Fabsolute pillar of the community he's
OL,11,Fdone so much for the community around
OL,12,FCastle Douglas and Loch Ken"
OL,14,FMr McLelland has already raised almost
OL,15,F#9,000, all of which will support NHS
OL,16,Fstaff and services, and as he seeks to
OL,17,Fraise more, the community here is
OL,18,Frallying behind him.
